 104, 105, 106, 107, 108, 109, 110]}, {"id": 26, "text": "(Portugal)", "words": [111]}, {"id": 27, "text": "3.", "words": [112]}, {"id": 28, "text": "- Quels livres lisiez-vous quand vous étiez adolescent(e) ?", "words": [113, 114, 115, 116, 117, 118, 119, 120, 121]}, {"id": 29, "text": "(livres d'aventures)", "words": [122, 123]}, {"id": 30, "text": "4.", "words": [124]}, {"id": 31, "text": "- Quels sports faisiez-vous au lycée ?", "words": [125, 126, 127, 128, 129, 130, 131]}, {"id": 32, "text": "(volley)", "words": [132]}, {"id": 33, "text": "5.", "words": [133]}, {"id": 34, "text": "- Qu'est-ce que vous preniez au petit déjeuner ?", "words": [134, 135, 136, 137, 138, 139, 140, 141, 142]}, {"id": 35, "text": "(café au lait)", "words": [143, 144, 145]}, {"id": 36, "text": "6.", "words": [146]}, {"id": 37, "text": "- Quelle musique écoutiez-vous ?", "words": [147, 148, 149, 150, 151]}, {"id": 38, "text": "(Michael Jackson)", "words": [152, 153]}, {"id": 39, "text": "7.", "words": [154]}, {"id": 40, "text": "- Que vouliez-vous faire plus tard comme métier ?", "words": [155, 156, 157, 158, 159, 160, 161, 162, 163]}, {"id": 41, "text": "(architecte)", "words": [164]}, {"id": 42, "text": "Complétez à l'imparfait.", "words": [165, 166, 167]}, {"id": 43, "text": "Quand j'étais petit, unchien.", "words": [168, 169, 170, 171]}, {"id": 44, "text": "La nuit, il dans monlit.", "words": [172, 173, 174, 175, 176]}, {"id": 45, "text": "fier de lui.", "words": [177, 178, 179]}, {"id": 46, "text": "grandes oreilles.", "words": [180, 181]}, {"id": 47, "text": "Le matin, quand à", "words": [182, 183, 184, 185]}, {"id": 48, "text": "l'école, il avec moi.", "words": [186, 187, 188, 189]}, {"id": 49, "text": "adorable.", "words": [190]}]}